  "randompranks": {
    "script": "this is in development, revision #21.6 (random multipitching works!!)\n {iscript:\nload {iv} a\nload https://youtu.be/gRcj6CAhe7s dirt\n{set:snip|{range:700|7200}/100}\n{set:snip2|{math:{get:snip}+{range:1|500}/100}\nd=$(ffprobe -i $FILE_1 -show_entries format=duration -v quiet -of csv=\"p=0\")\n\nffmpeg -i \"$FILE_1\" -vf trim=start={get:snip},trim=end={get:snip2} -af atrim=start={get:snip},atrim=end={get:snip2} output/snip.mp4\n\nspeed dirt {range:25|1000}/100\nvolume dirt {range:50|1000}/100\nget a width w\nget a height h\nget a duration d\ncopy dirt z\naudiopitch dirt {range:170|2000}/1000\naudiopitch dirt {range:170|2000}/1000\n{set:pitch|1}\n{foreach:{range:0|6}|copy z {get:pitch}\naudiopitch {get:pitch} {range:170|2000}/1000\naudiopitch {get:pitch} {range:170|2000}/1000\naudioputmix dirt {get:pitch}\n{set:pitch|{math:{get:pitch}+1}}}\nrepeatduration dirt d\n{choose:audiodestroy|haah|hooh|waaw|woow} a\n{choose:waves a {math:(({range:-10000|10000}/10000)^3)*100} w/({range:-1000|1000}/100) {range:100|1000}/100\nrotate a 90\nwaves a {math:(({range:-10000|10000}/10000)^3)*100} h/({range:-1000|1000}/100) {range:100|1000}/100\nrotate a -90|rotate a 90\nwaves a {math:(({range:-10000|10000}/10000)^3)*100} w/({range:-1000|1000}/100) {range:100|1000}/100\nrotate a -90\nwaves a {math:(({range:-10000|10000}/10000)^3)*100} h/({range:-1000|1000}/100) {range:100|1000}/100}\nhueshifthsv a {range:0|36000}/100 {range:-10000|10000}/100 {range:-10000|10000}/100\n{choose:audiodestroy|haah|hooh|waaw|woow} a\n{choose:audiodestroy|flip|flop} a\ncover a w h\nrepeatduration dirt d\naudioputreplace a dirt\nrender a\n}",
    "ownerId": "958167624133521488",
    "ownerUsername": "mr.media2k",
    "createdAt": "2026-06-30T06:30:35.043Z",
    "updatedAt": "2026-07-07T05:17:33.877Z"
  },
